# Stage 1 - Notification System Design

# Notification System REST API Design

## Objective

Design a REST API that allows the frontend to retrieve, manage, and receive real-time notifications for authenticated users.

---

# Assumptions

- Every user is authenticated using JWT.
- Notifications are user-specific.
- Users can:
  - View notifications
  - Read notification details
  - Mark notifications as read
  - Mark all notifications as read
  - Delete notifications
- The system supports real-time notifications using WebSockets.

---

# Base URL

```
https://api.example.com/api/v1
```

---

# Authentication Header

Every request requires:

```
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
```

---

