# API Endpoints

## 1. Get All Notifications

### Endpoint

```
GET /notifications
```

### Query Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| page | Integer | Page number |
| limit | Integer | Number of records |
| unreadOnly | Boolean | Return only unread notifications |

Example

```
GET /notifications?page=1&limit=10
```

### Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "notif_101",
      "title": "Assignment Submitted",
      "message": "Your assignment was submitted successfully.",
      "type": "success",
      "isRead": false,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-30T08:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "pagination": {
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 10,
    "total": 52
  }
}
```

Status Code

```
200 OK
```

---

