# Error Response Format

```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "NOT_FOUND",
    "message": "Notification not found."
  }
}
```

Common Status Codes

| Status | Meaning |
|---------|----------|
|200|Success|
|201|Created|
|204|Deleted Successfully|
|400|Bad Request|
|401|Unauthorized|
|403|Forbidden|
|404|Notification Not Found|
|500|Internal Server Error|

